### {109}{}{Well, this is an old gas station. It was built a long time ago... My grandpa built it as a matter of fact. It's one of the last gas stations of this kind around these here parts. Heh, and the bad part is... Those pumps are empty if you wanna know. Sometimes even months pass until someone stops by. Business was good while those caravans were still coming, I really don't know what happened to them. Even an old, rusty gas station like this costs me money...}
{109}{}{这是一个旧的加油站。它是很久以前建的。。。事实上是我爷爷建的。这是这里最后一个加油站。嘿，糟糕的是…如果你想知道的话，那些水泵是空的。有时甚至几个月过去了，直到有人路过。当那些大篷车还在来的时候，生意很好，我真的不知道他们发生了什么。即使是像这样一个老旧生锈的加油站也要我花钱。。。}
