{115}{}{你肯定有很多问题，老人家。}
### {116}{}{I've adopted him. His parents left him, few years ago. Actually, there was a rumor his parents were killed because of some debts. Nobody really knows what happened to them. They disappeared just like that. [Snaps his fingers.] Anyway, I'm trying to raise him as best as I can. Now he's helping me running this gas station. To me, he'll always be my little boy.}
{116}{}{我收养了他。他的父母几年前就离开了他。事实上，有传言说他的父母是因为一些债务而被杀害的。没有人真正知道他们发生了什么。他们就这样消失了。[拍他的手指。]不管怎样，我正在尽力把他养大。现在他在帮我经营这个加油站。对我来说，他永远是我的小儿子。}
